data.title: The Penguins of Madagascar S01E27 Ending Credits
data.meta_description: The Penguins of Madagascar S01E27 Ending Credits - Free download as Powerpoint Presentation (.ppt / .pptx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document lists the production crew for an animated television special titled "Halloween Thunderstorm". It includes over 100 roles such as the supervising producer, animation producer, character designers, voice actors, animators, lighting and effects artists, sound engineers, and more. The production involved teams in both the United States and India.
